WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.410 --> 02:50.000
[Episode 30]

03:17.230 --> 03:18.670
I was just following the sound.

03:18.690 --> 03:19.829
I didn't mean to disturb you.

03:19.850 --> 03:21.170
No worries.

03:21.430 --> 03:23.430
Tonight’s moon and stars are reminiscent of the ones

03:23.450 --> 03:25.960
I saw back in the Divine Region.

03:26.020 --> 03:27.190
It reminds me of

03:27.190 --> 03:28.980
people and events from

03:29.200 --> 03:30.000
a long time ago.

03:31.070 --> 03:32.210
I...

03:33.030 --> 03:34.540
You don't have to feel guilty.

03:34.579 --> 03:36.000
I harbor no other intentions.

03:36.350 --> 03:38.740
It's just that seeing you these past two days

03:38.770 --> 03:40.260
made me think of old friends who have passed.

03:57.579 --> 03:58.520
Fan Yue?

04:00.540 --> 04:01.590
Where could he have gone

04:01.620 --> 04:02.970
at this hour?

04:08.130 --> 04:09.690
We entered Bodhi Village by accident

04:09.710 --> 04:10.940
because we were looking for Old Turtle.

04:11.460 --> 04:13.070
Now that Old Turtle has been found,

04:13.220 --> 04:14.650
it's time for us to leave.

04:15.050 --> 04:16.079
Tomorrow morning,

04:16.269 --> 04:18.390
Bai Shuo and I will return to Bright Moon Palace.

04:18.410 --> 04:19.790
What's the rush?

04:20.010 --> 04:20.769
Master Fan,

04:20.800 --> 04:22.330
can't you stay for a few more days?

04:22.350 --> 04:23.640
You should understand that

04:23.750 --> 04:25.150
I already have someone in my heart.

04:25.680 --> 04:27.800
While I do feel guilty towards you,

04:28.330 --> 04:29.580
that's as far as it goes.

04:31.370 --> 04:32.470
Yes.

04:32.820 --> 04:34.020
You are not him after all.

04:35.880 --> 04:38.530
But you two have the exact same eyebrows.

04:43.960 --> 04:44.850
Ms. Bai?

04:45.680 --> 04:46.600
Shuo.

04:49.590 --> 04:51.150
We met by chance,

04:51.170 --> 04:52.800
not on purpose.

04:52.830 --> 04:55.270
Please don’t take it to heart.

04:55.290 --> 04:57.760
You don't need to keep explaining on behalf of Fan Yue.

04:57.790 --> 04:59.300
We've been through life and death,

04:59.320 --> 05:00.810
so of course I'll trust him fully.

05:02.140 --> 05:03.700
You and Master Fan are in perfect harmony with each other.

05:03.730 --> 05:05.050
I envy you.

05:05.080 --> 05:06.310
It's late.

05:06.390 --> 05:07.630
I'll get going.

05:08.260 --> 05:09.100
Divine Maiden.

05:11.450 --> 05:13.360
It has been so many years.

05:13.380 --> 05:15.460
If the Demon Lord is destined to never return,

05:15.610 --> 05:17.760
have you ever thought about leaving Bodhi Village

05:17.780 --> 05:19.980
and see the Eastern Continent of today,

05:20.010 --> 05:21.450
which you had protected back then?

05:22.900 --> 05:24.280
I've done what I set out to do

05:24.300 --> 05:25.940
60,000 years ago.

05:26.450 --> 05:28.330
Since Jing Yuan no longer exists in this world,

05:28.350 --> 05:31.350
there's no need for Xing Yue to exist either.

05:31.380 --> 05:33.700
Now I just want to protect this quiet place

05:33.720 --> 05:35.080
and reminisce the past.

05:35.530 --> 05:36.900
Perhaps in my heart,

05:36.920 --> 05:38.170
I'll always believe that

05:38.570 --> 05:40.040
as long as I don't forget him,

05:40.060 --> 05:41.990
he will live on in my heart forever.

05:52.760 --> 05:53.560
Do you feel sorry for her?

05:54.690 --> 05:55.130
No.

05:55.159 --> 05:56.110
I know.

05:56.780 --> 05:58.850
We've been through so much together.

05:58.870 --> 06:01.150
I won't doubt our relationship anymore.

06:01.800 --> 06:04.090
Even if your body holds some of the Demon Lord's memories,

06:04.560 --> 06:06.720
and that they may live longer than us

06:06.740 --> 06:08.060
and are more powerful than us,

06:09.130 --> 06:11.210
the relationship we share

06:11.340 --> 06:13.170
is not any lighter or less profound

06:13.190 --> 06:14.600
than any other relationships in this world.

06:15.890 --> 06:18.180
I just feel that she seems really pitiful

06:18.690 --> 06:20.370
and I feel sorry for her.

06:23.000 --> 06:24.150
Shuo.

06:24.170 --> 06:25.040
Even a deity

06:25.070 --> 06:26.860
can't have everything go as they wish.

06:26.980 --> 06:28.220
Even if there's guilt,

06:28.250 --> 06:29.930
I should feel guilty, not you.

06:30.340 --> 06:33.100
I just want to find the last Contemplation

06:33.280 --> 06:35.790
and remove the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal on you.

06:38.710 --> 06:40.470
Love, hate, kill, greed, and kindness.

06:40.700 --> 06:42.310
Now only greed is left.

06:42.710 --> 06:44.670
But there is so much greed in this world.

06:45.510 --> 06:46.760
Love is a form of greed.

06:46.850 --> 06:48.140
Sin is a form of greed.

06:48.620 --> 06:49.740
Every want

06:49.770 --> 06:51.200
or desire is a form of greed.

06:51.740 --> 06:53.900
It may exist in any corner of the world

06:54.090 --> 06:56.330
or in anyone's heart.

06:57.490 --> 06:58.930
It's too vague.

06:58.960 --> 07:02.180
The first four Contemplations were all preceded by omens.

07:02.320 --> 07:04.250
I believe the fifth Contemplation will definitely appear.

07:06.890 --> 07:07.650
Fan Yue.

07:08.020 --> 07:10.690
I am sure we will be together forever.

07:28.530 --> 07:31.560
Someone actually hid this village with their spiritual power.

07:31.670 --> 07:34.590
I followed the hidden power in Chong Zhao's body to get here.

07:34.690 --> 07:36.300
It seems that Chong Zhao

07:36.330 --> 07:38.190
is in this village.

07:47.060 --> 07:48.650
Lanling Barrier?

08:00.470 --> 08:01.600
Divine power?

08:01.870 --> 08:03.380
It's been 60,000 years.

08:03.850 --> 08:05.840
Who would've thought

08:05.860 --> 08:08.070
the Hidden Race still existed in this world,

08:08.230 --> 08:10.560
though you've done a fine job disguising yourself as a demon.

08:15.390 --> 08:17.210
I also didn't expect that

08:17.400 --> 08:19.650
the Lotus Spirit

08:19.680 --> 08:21.590
still exists in this world.

08:21.610 --> 08:24.350
If a mere beast like you from the Hidden Race can live just fine,

08:24.380 --> 08:26.210
why can't I, who have basked in

08:26.230 --> 08:28.130
divine rays for thousands of years?

08:28.650 --> 08:30.250
Why are you here?

08:30.280 --> 08:32.120
I'm not sure what she's up to.

08:32.140 --> 08:34.070
I mustn't let her know Chong Zhao's identity.

08:35.860 --> 08:38.340
The Contemplation Stone is a sacred object of the Divine Race.

08:38.390 --> 08:40.030
Now, the person with the Contemplation Stone

08:40.030 --> 08:41.200
is in this village.

08:41.610 --> 08:42.409
I...

08:42.440 --> 08:43.900
came for her of course.

08:43.940 --> 08:45.420
If you hand over the people who had just entered the village,

08:45.450 --> 08:48.090
Considering we're both from the Divine Race,

08:48.110 --> 08:49.160
I can

08:49.190 --> 08:50.990
spare you this time.

08:57.680 --> 09:00.320
Back when I transformed into a spirit next to the Demon Lord,

09:00.350 --> 09:02.540
you haven't even gained spiritual consciousness.

09:02.560 --> 09:03.880
Do you really think

09:03.900 --> 09:05.850
you are my match?

09:05.880 --> 09:08.570
On the account of our old ties from back then,

09:08.590 --> 09:10.950
I'll let you off the hook today.

09:10.980 --> 09:13.740
Don't even think about hurting any of these villagers.

09:13.760 --> 09:14.870
They...

09:14.940 --> 09:16.540
are all mine.

09:17.540 --> 09:18.610
Get lost!

09:23.690 --> 09:26.210
I have yet to fully recover.

09:26.230 --> 09:27.620
I can't simply barge in.

09:28.210 --> 09:29.440
Looks like

09:29.650 --> 09:31.980
I'll have to start with this Lanling Barrier.

09:40.050 --> 09:41.740
I have bid farewell to Luan Zhu last night.

09:41.770 --> 09:43.250
There's no need to greet her again.

09:43.270 --> 09:45.100
But what are your plans for

09:45.130 --> 09:46.410
Fu Ling and Chong Zhao?

09:47.150 --> 09:49.000
Chong Zhao just reunited with his parents.

09:49.000 --> 09:50.840
I'm sure he'll want to stay here for a few more days.

09:51.450 --> 09:52.630
As for Fu Ling...

09:52.870 --> 09:53.960
Ms. Bai!

09:53.980 --> 09:55.020
Ms. Bai!

09:55.150 --> 09:56.750
Mis. Bai, your master..

09:56.780 --> 09:57.780
What happened to my master?

09:57.800 --> 09:59.370
Your master went out to collect herbs early in the morning

09:59.400 --> 10:00.830
and accidentally fell off the cliff.

10:00.850 --> 10:02.510
He even broke his turtle shell!

10:06.800 --> 10:07.710
Master!

10:10.510 --> 10:11.320
My disciple!

10:11.320 --> 10:13.200
You're finally here.

10:14.020 --> 10:14.970
How are you feeling?

10:15.030 --> 10:18.080
I'm afraid today is the last time you and I

10:18.080 --> 10:19.510
will see each other.

10:19.510 --> 10:20.790
It hurts so much!

10:20.790 --> 10:22.080
Don't talk nonsense.

10:25.760 --> 10:27.450
Your turtle shell is so badly cracked.

10:27.480 --> 10:28.150
Where is your medicine?

10:28.150 --> 10:29.030
I'll apply it for you.

10:29.740 --> 10:31.360
We are not at Lanling,

10:31.360 --> 10:32.270
so I have no medicine.

10:32.270 --> 10:34.910
That's also why I went up the mountain to collect herbs,

10:34.910 --> 10:38.170
only to fall off from the cliff.

10:40.360 --> 10:41.080
Fan Yue.

10:41.080 --> 10:42.170
Please take care of Master for me.

10:42.210 --> 10:42.970
I'll go up the mountain to collect herbs.

10:43.000 --> 10:43.790
I'll go with you.

10:43.910 --> 10:44.670
No, no!

10:44.670 --> 10:46.200
You mustn't leave me all alone.

10:46.200 --> 10:47.320
At least one of you

10:47.320 --> 10:49.260
should stay behind with me.

10:49.290 --> 10:50.930
What if some bad guys come in?

10:50.950 --> 10:54.240
There's nothing I can do now.

10:54.780 --> 10:55.870
You don't know anything about medicine,

10:55.870 --> 10:56.750
so I should go.

10:56.750 --> 10:57.730
You stay and take care of Master.

10:57.750 --> 10:58.540
But you...

11:02.000 --> 11:03.230
I'll be right back!

11:34.200 --> 11:34.870
Be careful, Shuo!

11:44.290 --> 11:45.480
Be careful, Shuo!

11:47.980 --> 11:49.840
Thank goodness I have you, Xi.

11:52.010 --> 11:52.890
Don't be afraid.

11:52.920 --> 11:54.280
As long as I'm here,

11:54.300 --> 11:55.700
no matter what happens,

11:55.730 --> 11:57.570
I'll be at your side in no time

11:57.590 --> 11:58.400
and protect you.

11:58.700 --> 12:03.450
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

12:06.820 --> 12:12.450
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

12:13.840 --> 12:15.200
That carnivorous flower

12:15.110 --> 12:22.660
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

12:15.220 --> 12:17.060
is commonly seen in the Eternal and Demon Races.

12:17.090 --> 12:17.750
With just a moment of inattention,

12:17.750 --> 12:18.600
you'll be eaten alive

12:18.600 --> 12:20.310
once you get caught.

12:20.340 --> 12:22.410
If you've nothing better to do, can you stop running around?

12:22.430 --> 12:24.000
What did you just call me?

12:23.460 --> 12:28.700
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

12:27.180 --> 12:28.510
Why did you save me?

12:41.590 --> 12:42.710
I remember you asked me

12:43.310 --> 12:45.550
about this dagger back in the Fox Clan.

12:48.060 --> 12:51.470
♫Across thousands of miles♫

12:55.480 --> 12:57.430
I can tell you now.

12:56.390 --> 13:01.080
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

12:57.790 --> 12:58.850
This dagger

12:58.870 --> 13:00.660
was a gift from my sister, Bai Xi.

13:03.710 --> 13:10.980
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

13:07.230 --> 13:08.110
Your dagger

13:08.130 --> 13:09.330
has nothing to do with me.

13:09.350 --> 13:10.720
Xi said

13:11.300 --> 13:12.860
no matter what happens to me,

13:12.050 --> 13:16.720
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

13:12.950 --> 13:15.410
she would be by my side immediately.

13:15.660 --> 13:17.090
She also said

13:17.270 --> 13:18.600
as long as she's by my side,

13:18.600 --> 13:19.850
I don't have to be afraid.

13:19.800 --> 13:25.800
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

13:19.870 --> 13:21.160
So what?

13:21.650 --> 13:23.780
I've told you that Bai Xi is dead,

13:23.870 --> 13:24.790
but you refuse to believe me.

13:24.790 --> 13:26.390
Then why did you show up?

13:27.110 --> 13:28.810
Why did you save me?

13:28.130 --> 13:33.950
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

13:28.840 --> 13:30.360
If you are Fu Ling,

13:30.450 --> 13:32.250
you would've wanted me dead.

13:34.760 --> 13:35.560
I was just passing by,

13:35.580 --> 13:37.830
and now I’m being questioned on my occasional kindness.

13:36.680 --> 13:43.740
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

13:37.850 --> 13:39.780
It seems like I should be even nastier.

13:40.700 --> 13:42.980
Let me tell you one last time.

13:43.020 --> 13:45.120
I'm not Bai Xi.

13:44.450 --> 13:49.300
♫I'm your wanderer♫

13:45.140 --> 13:46.090
If you want to dream on,

13:46.120 --> 13:47.410
get lost!

13:49.520 --> 13:51.010
Stop pestering me.

13:52.620 --> 13:56.630
♫The flowers flew away♫

13:57.040 --> 13:57.940
Shuo.

13:58.870 --> 14:00.470
I've let both you

14:00.180 --> 14:04.300
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

14:00.940 --> 14:02.420
and Father down.

14:03.270 --> 14:05.300
How could I ever acknowledge you?

14:06.950 --> 14:09.220
Besides, the Heart Devouring Poison is incurable.

14:08.880 --> 14:15.860
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

14:09.280 --> 14:11.280
The poison will relapse in a month once I stop my medicine.

14:12.290 --> 14:14.420
I don't have much days left to live.

14:15.050 --> 14:16.400
Even if we acknowledge each other,

14:16.930 --> 14:18.760
so what?

14:16.990 --> 14:22.170
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

14:28.430 --> 14:29.580
How is Master?

14:29.660 --> 14:30.660
He's fine for now.

14:30.690 --> 14:31.810
He just fell asleep.

14:33.950 --> 14:35.150
What's wrong?

14:35.180 --> 14:36.340
You look troubled.

14:37.600 --> 14:39.690
When I was gathering herbs in the mountain just now,

14:39.900 --> 14:41.500
I happened to encounter a carnivorous flower.

14:41.540 --> 14:42.970
Carnivorous flower?

14:42.990 --> 14:44.160
Are you hurt?

14:44.780 --> 14:46.680
I'm fine. Don't worry.

14:48.630 --> 14:49.150
It was...

14:49.940 --> 14:51.970
Ful Ling who appeared in time

14:52.000 --> 14:53.170
and saved me.

14:53.930 --> 14:55.440
Fu Ling?

14:55.640 --> 14:57.210
If she wasn't Xi,

14:57.230 --> 14:59.140
why would she risk her life to save me?

14:59.170 --> 15:01.260
But she refuses to admit that she is Xi.

15:01.900 --> 15:03.290
There are too many things

15:03.450 --> 15:04.730
standing between the both of you.

15:05.400 --> 15:06.890
If I were her,

15:06.920 --> 15:08.470
perhaps I wouldn't dare to acknowledge you either.

15:09.770 --> 15:11.160
Give her some time,

15:11.340 --> 15:13.020
and also give yourself some time too.

15:16.800 --> 15:18.590
I'll go make medicine for Master first.

15:30.240 --> 15:32.790
If I had known it was so dangerous,

15:32.820 --> 15:35.790
I wouldn't have let you go up the mountain to collect herbs.

15:37.300 --> 15:40.410
Isn't Fu Ling your rival?

15:40.440 --> 15:42.910
Why did she save you?

15:42.950 --> 15:44.520
Could it be that...

15:44.630 --> 15:46.200
she found her conscience and wants to turn over a new leaf?

15:49.520 --> 15:50.690
My disciple,

15:50.720 --> 15:51.900
what's wrong?

15:52.220 --> 15:53.140
Master.

15:54.140 --> 15:55.210
People often say that

15:55.270 --> 15:57.480
there is no greater virtue than recognizing one's mistakes and making amends.

15:57.860 --> 15:59.030
But if someone

15:59.030 --> 16:00.750
made a really huge mistake,

16:00.780 --> 16:01.970
can they still turn things around?

16:06.900 --> 16:09.510
You keep asking me such tough questions.

16:09.650 --> 16:12.530
I don't know who you're talking about,

16:12.660 --> 16:14.350
but I think

16:14.380 --> 16:15.320
in this world,

16:15.320 --> 16:17.850
not everyone have choices.

16:17.880 --> 16:19.480
Also, not everyone can

16:19.480 --> 16:21.630
live according to their wishes.

16:21.660 --> 16:22.750
Perhaps,

16:22.750 --> 16:25.960
even the most despicable people have a pitiable side.

16:27.600 --> 16:28.480
My disciple,

16:29.180 --> 16:30.860
why are you suddenly asking such a question?

16:30.890 --> 16:32.800
Did Fan Yue bully you?

16:34.570 --> 16:35.880
No.

16:35.900 --> 16:36.880
It's Xi.

16:37.260 --> 16:38.260
Bai Xi?

16:38.290 --> 16:39.850
Your... your sister?

16:51.800 --> 16:52.610
Remember,

16:53.440 --> 16:55.320
don't mess with the wrong people.

16:58.470 --> 17:00.520
With you protecting Shuo,

17:00.540 --> 17:02.270
no one will bully her anymore.

17:02.770 --> 17:04.099
Why are you here?

17:04.130 --> 17:05.440
For the same reasons as you.

17:05.460 --> 17:06.450
I'm here to investigate.

17:07.119 --> 17:08.450
You also have your suspicions?

17:09.130 --> 17:10.980
There's a record of this village

17:11.000 --> 17:12.280
in my parents' handwritten journal.

17:25.430 --> 17:27.109
I was curious how this village

17:27.130 --> 17:29.370
could have disappeared so quickly in front of my parents,

17:29.400 --> 17:31.130
yet somehow, they were able to enter

17:31.150 --> 17:33.260
and remain hidden here for ten years afterwards.

17:34.300 --> 17:36.260
So do you trust this journal more,

17:36.790 --> 17:38.620
or do you trust them as they are now?

17:41.810 --> 17:43.190
I don't know.

17:43.360 --> 17:45.510
I'm even a little afraid to face the truth.

17:45.540 --> 17:47.300
Regardless which is real or fake,

17:47.940 --> 17:49.690
neither of it is a good outcome for me.

17:56.360 --> 17:58.940
You mean Fu Ling may be your sister?

17:59.180 --> 18:00.670
But I don't understand.

18:00.690 --> 18:02.280
If she were Xi,

18:02.300 --> 18:03.510
how could she have done that

18:03.510 --> 18:04.850
to our father?

18:04.870 --> 18:05.590
Unless

18:05.590 --> 18:07.230
she didn't know she's Xi herself.

18:07.760 --> 18:11.080
Do you want to confirm the real identity of Fu Ling?

18:12.120 --> 18:13.330
Do you have a way?

18:13.360 --> 18:14.880
Although I don't,

18:16.730 --> 18:19.060
but the Divine Maiden does.

18:23.460 --> 18:25.000
The Spirit Conjuration Cauldron?

18:25.050 --> 18:27.340
I heard from Master that you have this instrument

18:27.370 --> 18:29.020
that can verify kinship through a drop of blood.

18:29.300 --> 18:30.610
You want to verify kinship?

18:31.650 --> 18:32.860
I've got my own use for it.

18:32.890 --> 18:34.680
If you are willing to lend me this treasure of yours,

18:34.700 --> 18:36.260
I will definitely repay you.

18:36.290 --> 18:38.010
How will you repay me?

18:38.840 --> 18:40.320
What do you want?

18:40.340 --> 18:41.540
I will give you anything

18:41.570 --> 18:42.700
within my means.

18:44.260 --> 18:46.460
Since you are Fan Yue's lover,

18:46.480 --> 18:48.350
then you're also my friend.

18:48.380 --> 18:50.140
If you're my friend,

18:50.160 --> 18:52.560
how could I be stingy?

18:53.280 --> 18:55.520
This is the Spirit Conjuration Cauldron you are looking for.

18:55.540 --> 18:57.970
Simply drip your blood into the cauldron,

18:58.000 --> 18:59.000
and it will reveal

18:59.020 --> 19:01.790
your closest kin connected to you by blood.

19:02.700 --> 19:03.780
Thank you, Divine Maiden.

19:03.810 --> 19:05.640
I owe you a big favor today.

19:05.660 --> 19:06.790
That's not necessary.

19:06.820 --> 19:09.480
I hope you get the results you are hoping for.

19:18.160 --> 19:19.140
Come out.

19:24.130 --> 19:25.980
Congratulations, Divine Maiden.

19:26.030 --> 19:28.720
Your wish will come true soon.

19:29.090 --> 19:31.860
Looks like your cracked shell was worth it.

19:32.950 --> 19:33.840
For you, Divine Maiden,

19:33.870 --> 19:35.060
my injury...

19:36.090 --> 19:37.970
is nothing.

19:38.000 --> 19:39.370
But there's something

19:39.390 --> 19:40.630
I'm curious about.

19:40.660 --> 19:43.490
Why don't you just kill her?

19:44.500 --> 19:45.940
If I kill her,

19:45.970 --> 19:47.810
Fan Yue will remember her forever.

19:47.830 --> 19:49.590
Why should I bother myself?

19:50.610 --> 19:51.460
By the way,

19:51.490 --> 19:53.290
how is that old man?

19:53.600 --> 19:54.640
That old bastard

19:54.640 --> 19:56.880
is half dead by now.

20:04.000 --> 20:05.770
Once he's completely dead,

20:05.800 --> 20:08.320
you'll have him all to yourself.

20:08.600 --> 20:10.560
Whether it's his body, appearance,

20:10.590 --> 20:12.110
lifespan, destiny,

20:12.130 --> 20:14.610
or his alchemy and divination skills.

20:15.840 --> 20:19.000
Thank you for blessing me, Divine Maiden.

20:19.810 --> 20:20.940
For so many years,

20:20.960 --> 20:22.920
I only managed to maintain human form

20:22.920 --> 20:24.070
by absorbing the Eternals' spiritual energy.

20:24.090 --> 20:25.770
I'm tired of it.

20:25.800 --> 20:26.960
This time,

20:26.980 --> 20:29.330
I might as well find a way to solve it once and for all.

20:30.090 --> 20:31.440
But Heavenly Maiden,

20:31.460 --> 20:34.420
there’s still one more thing that I don’t understand.

20:34.450 --> 20:36.100
Although you and the Demon Lord

20:36.120 --> 20:37.360
were deeply in love,

20:37.390 --> 20:39.660
that was 60,000 years ago.

20:39.690 --> 20:41.620
The Demon Lord is no longer the Demon Lord from back then

20:41.640 --> 20:43.680
because Fan Yue has forgotten everything.

20:43.710 --> 20:45.160
Why do you...

20:45.180 --> 20:47.530
Why do you have to stay so obsessed with him?

20:47.550 --> 20:50.180
You're just a dummy made of silk.

20:50.210 --> 20:51.540
What would you know?

20:52.350 --> 20:54.700
He gave me life with his divine blood.

20:54.730 --> 20:56.600
His blood

20:56.620 --> 20:58.070
runs through my veins.

20:58.100 --> 20:59.860
Even after 60,000 years,

20:59.950 --> 21:01.900
even if he has forgotten everything,

21:01.930 --> 21:03.790
as long as I'm alive,

21:03.810 --> 21:05.570
every moment,

21:05.720 --> 21:07.440
this beating pulse,

21:07.470 --> 21:09.150
this flowing blood,

21:09.190 --> 21:11.150
this unbroken breath

21:11.220 --> 21:13.280
all remind me that

21:13.420 --> 21:15.180
I exist because of him.

21:15.940 --> 21:17.470
And he...

21:17.650 --> 21:18.880
can only...

21:18.900 --> 21:20.820
and must only be mine.

21:23.640 --> 21:24.510
Fu Ling.

21:25.200 --> 21:27.150
Are you really Xi?

21:27.400 --> 21:29.360
I have too many questions.

21:29.540 --> 21:31.060
If you are Xi,

21:31.090 --> 21:33.140
why did you transform into a demon from a human?

21:33.300 --> 21:35.460
And why did you force our father to death?

21:36.000 --> 21:37.070
Now,

21:37.140 --> 21:38.790
I want a clear answer.

22:21.470 --> 22:22.390
It's you.

22:24.040 --> 22:25.510
What did you do to me?

22:26.130 --> 22:28.000
You pricked yourself.

22:28.020 --> 22:29.590
What can I do?

22:31.120 --> 22:32.050
What is this?

22:33.610 --> 22:36.190
I came to tell you that

22:36.220 --> 22:38.010
I remembered it wrong.

22:38.040 --> 22:40.840
This Spirit Conjuration Cauldron is not meant for you to confirm your kinship,

22:40.860 --> 22:42.040
but it's meant for me

22:43.390 --> 22:45.100
to take your body.

22:45.130 --> 22:46.530
What do you mean?

22:46.550 --> 22:47.590
Don't fret.

22:47.620 --> 22:49.360
You'll know soon.

22:54.150 --> 22:56.070
Don't waste your breath.

22:56.100 --> 22:57.790
Your blood is in the cauldron.

22:57.810 --> 23:00.300
Your body has been controlled.

23:00.620 --> 23:01.910
So,

23:02.130 --> 23:03.830
you've been pretending this entire time.

23:04.300 --> 23:05.640
That's right.

23:05.680 --> 23:07.500
Since you entered Bodhi Village,

23:07.530 --> 23:08.770
I've been scheming.

23:08.790 --> 23:09.830
Do you know why

23:09.860 --> 23:11.580
attacked by the carnivorous flower

23:11.610 --> 23:14.090
and Fu Ling came coincidentally to save you?

23:14.530 --> 23:16.160
I know you've been guessing

23:16.160 --> 23:17.800
if Fu Ling is your sister or not.

23:17.830 --> 23:19.390
She doesn't admit it,

23:19.410 --> 23:20.980
but she's always watching you.

23:21.010 --> 23:22.640
So, I gave her a push

23:22.660 --> 23:24.680
to see if she'd save you.

23:24.850 --> 23:25.920
As expected,

23:25.940 --> 23:27.510
she saved you.

23:27.540 --> 23:28.710
In this way,

23:28.730 --> 23:31.060
you want to know her identity even more, right?

23:31.540 --> 23:34.170
You guided me step by step

23:34.830 --> 23:37.480
to finally borrow the Spirit Conjuration Cauldron from you.

23:39.430 --> 23:40.500
No.

23:41.400 --> 23:44.430
Master asked me to borrow the treasure from the Divine Maiden.

23:44.570 --> 23:46.030
He is not my master.

23:46.060 --> 23:48.070
You're so smart.

23:48.180 --> 23:49.940
Unfortunately, i's too late.

23:49.960 --> 23:52.800
The one you've been calling "Master" these days

23:52.830 --> 23:54.170
is just a fake person

23:54.200 --> 23:55.910
I made with thread.

23:55.930 --> 23:57.710
Where is my real master?

23:57.740 --> 23:59.220
He's also in Bodhi Village.

24:00.090 --> 24:01.460
Don't worry.

24:01.480 --> 24:03.140
You'll see him in the future.

24:03.260 --> 24:04.700
Now,

24:04.830 --> 24:07.040
let's settle our problem first.

24:56.020 --> 24:58.100
This body is mine.

24:58.710 --> 25:00.120
Fan Yue

25:00.150 --> 25:02.040
will be mine in the end too.

25:11.600 --> 25:12.600
Strange.

25:13.160 --> 25:15.270
Why is the mountain so foggy?

25:31.260 --> 25:33.700
The fog can't be erased even with spiritual power.

25:33.730 --> 25:35.880
It seems that it's not an ordinary barrier.

25:35.900 --> 25:38.030
This is the only way in and out of Bodhi Village.

25:38.060 --> 25:38.960
If the fog is still there,

25:38.960 --> 25:40.480
we won't be able to find the way out of the village.

25:42.310 --> 25:43.720
Let's go further.

25:44.780 --> 25:45.780
Fan Yue.

25:45.810 --> 25:47.000
Chong Zhao.

25:51.780 --> 25:52.920
Aren't you taking care of Old Turtle?

25:52.920 --> 25:53.690
Why are you here?

25:53.720 --> 25:54.760
Master has taken the medicine.

25:54.790 --> 25:56.240
He's fine now.

25:56.400 --> 25:57.830
I found you were missing.

25:57.830 --> 25:58.790
I was afraid you were not safe,

25:58.820 --> 25:59.990
so I came out to find you.

26:00.010 --> 26:01.360
What are you doing here?

26:01.390 --> 26:03.430
We think this village is strange.

26:03.450 --> 26:04.540
It's shrouded in fog.

26:04.570 --> 26:05.720
It seems we can't get out.

26:07.250 --> 26:08.270
All of this fog

26:08.270 --> 26:09.720
won't disperse so quickly.

26:09.720 --> 26:10.920
It's late now.

26:10.920 --> 26:12.510
It's more dangerous at night in the mountain.

26:12.510 --> 26:13.440
Why don't we go back first

26:13.440 --> 26:14.600
and wait till tomorrow?

26:14.620 --> 26:15.450
Okay.

26:17.380 --> 26:18.230
Let's go.

26:55.630 --> 26:57.470
Why did you suddenly go to the back mountain?

26:57.890 --> 26:59.440
That carnivorous flower dared to attack you.

26:59.470 --> 27:01.070
Of course I have to take revenge.

27:04.400 --> 27:06.560
The carnivorous flower is cruel.

27:06.580 --> 27:08.890
I don't want you to get hurt because of me.

27:11.730 --> 27:12.570
What's wrong?

27:14.490 --> 27:15.450
Nothing.

27:15.730 --> 27:17.440
I thought you would say I made a fuss.

27:17.460 --> 27:19.590
As a Demon King, I want to seek revenge on a flower.

27:19.620 --> 27:21.410
Are you unhappy

27:21.430 --> 27:22.710
I care about you?

27:23.130 --> 27:24.610
That's not what I meant.

27:24.640 --> 27:25.250
Sit down.

27:30.270 --> 27:31.400
I just feel

27:31.420 --> 27:33.400
everything in this village is strange.

27:33.430 --> 27:35.190
That's why I wanted to find out.

27:35.210 --> 27:36.510
Chong Zhao's parents disappeared for ten years

27:36.510 --> 27:37.880
and suddenly appeared here.

27:38.160 --> 27:39.530
Old Turtle fled here

27:39.560 --> 27:41.050
and fell off the cliff for no reason.

27:41.730 --> 27:43.290
The carnivorous flower suddenly attacked you.

27:43.320 --> 27:45.240
Now there's fog surrounding the village.

27:45.600 --> 27:47.810
All of these matters

27:47.840 --> 27:49.350
seem to be unrelated,

27:49.980 --> 27:52.460
but I think there must be something behind it.

27:52.480 --> 27:53.750
It's like...

27:54.330 --> 27:55.170
Like someone

27:55.200 --> 27:56.550
is trying to keep us here.

27:57.730 --> 27:59.400
Who do you think it is?

27:59.940 --> 28:01.610
If someone deliberately set up

28:01.640 --> 28:03.290
the fog surrounding the village

28:03.310 --> 28:05.400
and I can't dispel it even with my demonic power,

28:05.430 --> 28:06.720
then only one person in Bodhi Village

28:06.720 --> 28:07.960
could've done it.

28:09.250 --> 28:10.420
I'll go talk to her.

28:15.050 --> 28:16.300
It's getting dark.

28:17.150 --> 28:18.150
I'll be back soon.

28:35.370 --> 28:36.500
What did you find?

28:37.270 --> 28:38.380
There's heavy fog in the mountain.

28:38.410 --> 28:39.970
We can't find the way out of the village anymore.

28:39.990 --> 28:41.820
It's like a maze set up on purpose.

28:41.850 --> 28:42.860
Fog.

28:43.080 --> 28:44.520
Did you find anything else?

28:47.240 --> 28:48.680
Are you still

28:48.700 --> 28:50.710
suspicious of your parents?

28:57.300 --> 28:58.930
You haven't seen each other for ten years.

28:58.960 --> 29:00.400
It's normal that there's a feeling

29:00.420 --> 29:01.500
of estrangement.

29:03.500 --> 29:04.780
We've been apart for too long.

29:04.900 --> 29:07.040
I should cherish every moment of reunion,

29:07.070 --> 29:08.750
but I don't feel natural intimacy

29:08.770 --> 29:10.610
from my heart toward them.

29:11.790 --> 29:12.590
Do you think it's my problem

29:12.590 --> 29:13.510
or theirs?

29:17.400 --> 29:18.070
Zhao,

29:18.070 --> 29:18.870
Ms. Fu Ling.

29:18.900 --> 29:20.470
Come in and eat.

29:20.510 --> 29:21.510
Coming.

29:28.720 --> 29:29.330
Here,

29:29.360 --> 29:30.000
Ms. Fu Ling.

29:30.000 --> 29:30.680
Thank you.

29:32.060 --> 29:32.990
Eat, Zhao.

29:39.990 --> 29:40.710
Zhao,

29:40.740 --> 29:41.820
why aren't you eating?

29:41.840 --> 29:44.080
Do you not like my cooking?

29:44.930 --> 29:45.580
No.

29:46.260 --> 29:48.060
I found heavy fog in the mountain

29:48.080 --> 29:49.750
and blocked the way out of the village.

29:49.780 --> 29:51.480
Do you know what this is?

29:52.930 --> 29:54.010
Heavy fog?

29:54.460 --> 29:57.010
Maybe it's because of the bad weather.

29:58.710 --> 30:00.430
Why? Are you leaving?

30:01.330 --> 30:03.090
Chong Zhao just reunited with you.

30:03.120 --> 30:04.600
How could he bear to leave?

30:05.160 --> 30:06.190
That's good.

30:06.220 --> 30:07.220
That's good.

30:08.020 --> 30:09.230
-Let’s eat.
-Let’s eat.

30:11.880 --> 30:13.630
Do you really want us to stay?

30:14.890 --> 30:16.810
What are you talking about?

30:16.880 --> 30:18.680
Your mother and I haven't seen you for ten years.

30:18.680 --> 30:19.800
Now we finally meet again.

30:19.820 --> 30:21.730
Of course I hope to spend more time with you.

30:21.760 --> 30:23.410
Why don't we go together?

30:23.440 --> 30:25.350
Going back to Lanling or Ning'an City,

30:25.380 --> 30:26.440
you can still hide your identity

30:26.460 --> 30:27.500
and live an ordinary life.

30:31.720 --> 30:32.610
Zhao,

30:32.640 --> 30:34.920
your father and I have lived here for ten years.

30:34.960 --> 30:35.940
We're used to it.

30:35.960 --> 30:36.960
We don't want the trouble anymore.

30:36.990 --> 30:38.160
You were in Lanling for 100 years,

30:38.200 --> 30:39.360
but you could give it up easily.

30:39.390 --> 30:40.590
You've only lived here for ten years.

30:40.590 --> 30:41.310
Why...

30:41.310 --> 30:42.400
What can't you let go?

30:42.920 --> 30:44.270
Or are you afraid of something?

30:47.480 --> 30:48.150
Mother,

30:48.880 --> 30:50.200
you met Bai Xi when you were

30:50.200 --> 30:51.240
running away back then, right?

30:51.240 --> 30:51.830
Why did you ask her to tell me

30:51.830 --> 30:53.680
not to go back to Lanling?

30:53.710 --> 30:55.400
Who is after you?

30:55.420 --> 30:57.410
Which sect? Which group? Who?

30:59.510 --> 31:00.830
You won't forget the enemy that

31:00.830 --> 31:01.880
wanted to kill you, right?

31:01.910 --> 31:02.910
Father.

31:02.930 --> 31:04.210
You and Master were close.

31:04.240 --> 31:05.400
Does Master know you're hiding in

31:05.400 --> 31:06.390
Bodhi Village?

31:08.740 --> 31:09.740
Chong Zhao.

31:11.650 --> 31:13.450
So what do you mean?

31:14.000 --> 31:15.560
Do you know what you're doing?

31:15.580 --> 31:17.240
You're interrogating your parents.

31:17.260 --> 31:18.640
You're doubting your Master.

31:18.640 --> 31:20.190
I just want to know the truth.

31:20.220 --> 31:22.540
How did your mother and I teach you?

31:22.560 --> 31:23.890
It's only been ten years.

31:24.210 --> 31:26.440
Have you forgotten the most basic filial piety?

31:26.710 --> 31:28.070
I'm so angry.

31:32.840 --> 31:34.740
Why are you mad at him?

31:40.290 --> 31:41.120
Enough.

31:41.150 --> 31:42.300
Stop pretending.

31:43.500 --> 31:44.720
He's already suspicious.

31:44.720 --> 31:45.540
What should we do now?

31:45.590 --> 31:46.960
Don't be nervous. The Divine Maiden said

31:46.960 --> 31:48.240
it's normal for them to be suspicious.

31:48.270 --> 31:49.750
As long as she's not angry,

31:49.770 --> 31:50.910
everything will be fine.

31:52.330 --> 31:54.770
I hope the Divine Maiden can get what she wants soon.

31:54.790 --> 31:56.210
Only when she is happy

31:56.240 --> 31:58.020
can our lives be easier.

32:06.620 --> 32:08.690
I know you have a lot of doubts,

32:08.720 --> 32:11.110
but you were too emotional just now.

32:11.820 --> 32:13.130
I didn't want to get emotional,

32:14.020 --> 32:15.550
but I couldn't help it.

32:15.850 --> 32:18.460
I wish everything can go back to how it was.

32:19.210 --> 32:21.160
But why is it the more I ask, the more wrong it feels?

32:21.680 --> 32:22.960
My father used to teach me

32:22.960 --> 32:24.400
to persuade people with reason,

32:24.430 --> 32:26.300
instead of volume and status.

32:26.530 --> 32:29.000
But he threatened me with filial piety just now.

32:29.500 --> 32:31.220
He's trying to avoid things.

32:32.260 --> 32:34.510
Maybe there's a natural instinct when facing one's family.

32:35.740 --> 32:36.610
I think

32:37.630 --> 32:39.060
they are not my parents.

32:40.190 --> 32:41.670
But if they are fake,

32:41.690 --> 32:43.210
why would they do that?

32:43.230 --> 32:44.300
And why do they

32:44.330 --> 32:46.000
look exactly like your parents?

32:47.160 --> 32:48.710
I've observed them these days.

32:48.730 --> 32:49.850
The two of them

32:49.880 --> 32:51.310
are not disguised

32:51.530 --> 32:53.390
nor created with Eternal power.

32:54.880 --> 32:57.440
Have you heard that there was a secret technique in ancient times?

32:58.780 --> 33:00.050
Puppetry.

33:18.110 --> 33:19.420
No trespassing

33:19.450 --> 33:20.810
the Divine Maiden's room.

33:20.840 --> 33:21.910
Who are you?

33:21.930 --> 33:23.510
I'm the only doctor in Bodhi Village,

33:23.400 --> 33:25.340
[Qin Jiang, doctor of Bodhi Village]

33:23.510 --> 33:24.420
Qin Jiang.

33:24.450 --> 33:25.400
The Divine Maiden is sick.

33:25.400 --> 33:26.610
She won't see any guests for now.

33:26.630 --> 33:27.630
Please leave.

33:27.660 --> 33:28.460
Sick?

33:28.840 --> 33:29.760
Coincidentally,

33:30.400 --> 33:32.000
there are many elixirs in Bright Moon Palace.

33:32.030 --> 33:34.560
Let me see what ailment she has

33:34.580 --> 33:35.730
so that I can treat her.

33:43.460 --> 33:45.570
She just fell asleep after taking the medicine.

33:45.600 --> 33:46.920
Please leave.

33:59.550 --> 34:02.770
Fan Yue!

34:04.290 --> 34:05.850
What's wrong with her?

34:05.870 --> 34:07.210
The Bodhi Village

34:07.230 --> 34:08.699
is protected by the Divine Maiden.

34:08.750 --> 34:12.020
All the food and water in the village are made by the Divine Maiden.

34:12.120 --> 34:14.000
She used too much of her spiritual power

34:14.020 --> 34:15.350
and needs to sleep and rest.

34:15.370 --> 34:16.820
She will wake up in a few days.

34:16.850 --> 34:18.080
So,

34:18.100 --> 34:20.050
she set up the fog around the village?

34:20.210 --> 34:22.290
She knew she was going to fall into deep slumber.

34:22.320 --> 34:23.330
She was worried that

34:23.360 --> 34:25.480
something would happen in Bodhi Village without her protection.

34:25.510 --> 34:26.880
That's why she set up the fog

34:26.880 --> 34:28.310
to stop people from entering and exiting.

34:28.340 --> 34:30.219
The Divine Maiden did this for the sake of the villagers.

34:30.239 --> 34:31.480
When she wakes up a few days later,

34:31.480 --> 34:32.840
she'll undo the fog.

34:33.210 --> 34:34.210
But now,

34:34.230 --> 34:35.500
please leave.

34:35.530 --> 34:37.429
Don't disturb her rest.

34:40.960 --> 34:41.730
Fan Yue.

34:41.750 --> 34:42.710
Don't believe her.

34:46.070 --> 34:47.110
Fan Yue!

34:51.110 --> 34:52.150
Fan Yue.

34:57.250 --> 34:59.350
Your power and divine soul have been imprisoned

34:59.370 --> 35:00.870
by the Divine Maiden.

35:01.250 --> 35:02.850
No matter how loudly you shout,

35:02.880 --> 35:04.110
he won't hear you.

35:04.130 --> 35:06.070
Just lie there obediently.

35:22.780 --> 35:24.440
How did it go?

35:25.890 --> 35:27.240
Luan Zhu is sleeping.

35:27.270 --> 35:28.760
She'll wake up in a few days.

35:28.790 --> 35:29.970
Do you believe it?

35:30.620 --> 35:31.290
No.

35:32.510 --> 35:34.160
With your personality,

35:34.180 --> 35:36.090
you should've gotten to the bottom of things.

35:36.120 --> 35:37.950
Why did you come back?

35:37.970 --> 35:39.180
Could it be

35:39.210 --> 35:41.610
you still care about your relationship with her 60,000 years ago?

35:41.630 --> 35:42.310
No.

35:42.340 --> 35:43.240
I know.

35:43.690 --> 35:44.850
I'm just kidding.

35:46.370 --> 35:47.490
It's getting late.

35:47.510 --> 35:48.720
Go to bed early.

35:48.750 --> 35:50.060
We can resolve

35:50.080 --> 35:51.680
tomorrow's matters tomorrow.

36:02.080 --> 36:03.850
This is your first time helping me undress.

36:06.770 --> 36:07.770
Isn't it good?

36:08.620 --> 36:09.500
It's okay.

36:09.650 --> 36:10.750
I can do it myself.

36:16.700 --> 36:17.780
He's here.

36:18.490 --> 36:19.960
I suddenly remembered

36:20.670 --> 36:22.280
Master hasn't taken his medicine tonight.

36:22.440 --> 36:23.850
I'll go check on him.

36:24.350 --> 36:25.640
Get some rest.

36:25.670 --> 36:27.190
I'll be back soon.

36:53.590 --> 36:55.560
Sect Leader, do you want to kill me?

36:57.850 --> 36:59.580
What do you think about

37:00.090 --> 37:01.170
my new skin?

37:05.560 --> 37:07.010
Divine Maiden,

37:07.040 --> 37:08.730
you took Bai Shuo's body.

37:08.750 --> 37:10.900
Did Fan Yue notice it?

37:10.930 --> 37:12.050
What?

37:12.070 --> 37:13.950
Are you questioning my ability?

37:13.970 --> 37:14.860
I dare not.

37:14.890 --> 37:16.710
You are all-powerful.

37:16.730 --> 37:18.000
I’m just curious

37:18.030 --> 37:20.110
how you switched bodies with Bai Shuo

37:20.130 --> 37:21.920
without anyone knowing?

37:21.940 --> 37:23.190
Don't ask

37:23.220 --> 37:24.660
what you shouldn't ask.

37:24.890 --> 37:27.330
Divine Maiden, why did you suddenly

37:27.350 --> 37:28.390
summon me here today?

37:28.420 --> 37:30.270
I exchanged with Bai Shuo

37:30.290 --> 37:31.850
and used up a lot of spiritual power.

37:31.880 --> 37:33.230
I need some nourishment.

37:33.260 --> 37:35.280
Send some new Eternals in.

37:37.460 --> 37:38.540
You're unwilling?

37:40.880 --> 37:41.920
Back then,

37:41.950 --> 37:44.550
Fan Yue came to our sect to steal the Contemplation Stone.

37:44.570 --> 37:46.340
I deliberately didn't stop him

37:46.370 --> 37:47.440
just to use him

37:47.440 --> 37:49.580
to help me find someone who can gather the Five Contemplations.

37:49.610 --> 37:51.850
Now, Bai Shuo has gathered four Contemplations.

37:51.870 --> 37:53.650
We're one step away from success.

37:53.680 --> 37:55.690
If you take her body now,

37:55.720 --> 37:57.610
the Five Contemplations won't be gathered.

37:57.640 --> 37:58.990
If we don't gather all five,

37:59.010 --> 38:01.690
we can't activate the power of the divine stone.

38:01.720 --> 38:03.860
All I want is Fan Yue.

38:03.880 --> 38:06.360
I don't care if the Contemplation Stone

38:06.380 --> 38:07.970
can be activated or not.

38:08.690 --> 38:09.860
Jin Yao,

38:09.890 --> 38:12.410
these years, I've taught you the secret mental cultivation methods,

38:12.430 --> 38:14.100
helped you cultivate with spiritual power,

38:14.150 --> 38:16.410
and made you the leader of the Eternals.

38:16.430 --> 38:18.320
You've gotten enough.

38:18.350 --> 38:19.710
You're still not satisfied?

38:19.730 --> 38:21.810
You still want the power of the Contemplation Stone?

38:22.710 --> 38:23.880
Those who are too greedy

38:23.880 --> 38:25.710
don't meet good endings.

38:25.770 --> 38:27.650
Stay in your place.

38:27.670 --> 38:30.550
Don't forget that I gave you everything you have today.

38:30.580 --> 38:32.570
I can take it back anytime.

39:07.530 --> 39:09.600
Do you really want to die?

39:11.320 --> 39:12.030
Who is it?

39:17.640 --> 39:19.470
You can hear my voice?

39:19.740 --> 39:21.060
For so many years,

39:21.090 --> 39:22.480
you're the first one.

39:23.800 --> 39:24.910
Stop looking.

39:24.930 --> 39:26.430
I'm right in front of you.

39:28.400 --> 39:29.580
What demonic object are you?

39:30.420 --> 39:31.310
Demon?

39:44.670 --> 39:46.450
Do you really want to die?

39:46.550 --> 39:47.550
If you do,

39:47.580 --> 39:48.840
I can help you.

39:50.640 --> 39:52.120
Why don't you answer?

39:52.150 --> 39:53.360
You don't want to answer

39:53.390 --> 39:54.700
or do you not dare to?

39:54.720 --> 39:56.080
You don't dare to die

39:56.130 --> 39:57.450
nor do you want to die.

40:01.290 --> 40:02.640
Who are you?

40:03.100 --> 40:04.490
I'm not a demon

40:04.520 --> 40:05.880
nor an eternal.

40:06.220 --> 40:07.850
You should know

40:07.870 --> 40:10.200
there once was a Divine Race.

40:10.230 --> 40:11.340
Divine Race?

40:11.660 --> 40:12.560
You are...

40:31.920 --> 40:32.960
Jin Yao,

40:32.980 --> 40:34.670
I know everything about you.

40:34.700 --> 40:35.780
Your parents died young

40:35.810 --> 40:37.250
and your family was poor.

40:37.270 --> 40:39.630
You worked so hard to leave Bodhi Village

40:39.660 --> 40:41.530
and joined the Lanling Sect,

40:41.550 --> 40:44.110
but you were always oppressed by your peers because of your humble background.

40:44.140 --> 40:45.620
You were humiliated.

40:45.640 --> 40:46.950
You're in pain,

40:46.980 --> 40:48.150
right?

40:48.710 --> 40:50.350
Why?

40:50.380 --> 40:53.480
Why do some people have everything when they are born?

40:53.510 --> 40:55.070
I tried my best,

40:55.090 --> 40:57.010
but I still couldn't get a slightly fair chance.

40:57.070 --> 40:59.320
There is no fairness in this world.

40:59.340 --> 41:00.820
If you want to rise above others,

41:00.850 --> 41:01.960
I can help you.

41:01.980 --> 41:03.710
I can give you power,

41:03.740 --> 41:05.300
help you gain a foothold in Lanling,

41:05.320 --> 41:06.780
help you become the leader of the Eternals,

41:06.800 --> 41:09.510
and help you take revenge on those who bullied you.

41:09.540 --> 41:11.500
Whether it's a sinister and despicable Senior,

41:11.520 --> 41:13.440
or the unfair Master,

41:13.470 --> 41:14.920
as long as you want,

41:14.940 --> 41:17.220
they will all disappear from this world.

41:21.590 --> 41:23.710
Don't you want such a good opportunity?

41:24.460 --> 41:25.780
If not,

41:26.440 --> 41:27.400
then forget it.

41:27.430 --> 41:28.110
Wait.

41:29.510 --> 41:30.790
What's the condition?

41:31.410 --> 41:33.260
What do you want me to do?

41:33.280 --> 41:35.450
Sixty thousand years ago in the war of the Divine Region,

41:35.480 --> 41:36.830
my spiritual soul was damaged.

41:36.850 --> 41:38.480
I was in deep slumber until now.

41:38.550 --> 41:40.440
I need to absorb the spiritual energy of Eternals

41:40.440 --> 41:42.260
to maintain a human form.

41:42.280 --> 41:45.290
You just need to give some Eternals to me regularly.

41:47.860 --> 41:49.340
It's just a little favor.

41:49.370 --> 41:51.120
I don't need you to sacrifice anything.

41:51.480 --> 41:52.870
You just need to

41:53.660 --> 41:55.830
forget your conscience.

41:56.040 --> 41:57.360
That's all.

42:05.480 --> 42:06.740
I will

42:06.770 --> 42:08.300
always remember your kindness.

42:08.320 --> 42:10.240
I dare not have improper thoughts.

42:10.270 --> 42:11.890
But there is one more thing

42:11.910 --> 42:13.200
I need your help with.

42:13.230 --> 42:14.110
What is it?

42:14.590 --> 42:15.920
When I was capturing

42:15.920 --> 42:17.690
Chong Tai and Meng Ning back then,

42:17.720 --> 42:21.120
I accidentally met Bai Shuo's sister, Bai Xi.

42:27.080 --> 42:28.040
Father!

42:28.070 --> 42:29.790
I'm going to get Father to save Aunt Meng.

42:52.050 --> 42:55.220
Back then, Bai Xi was just a human child.

42:55.250 --> 42:57.750
She didn't die after being hit by me twice

42:58.030 --> 43:00.170
and became the current Fu Ling.

43:01.750 --> 43:03.990
She didn't die after two strikes?

43:04.010 --> 43:05.530
Interesting.

43:05.560 --> 43:06.480
I'm not sure

43:06.480 --> 43:08.670
if she saw my face or not.

43:09.330 --> 43:12.000
Divine Maiden, please kill Fu Ling and Chong Zhao

43:12.030 --> 43:13.840
in Bodhi Village.

43:14.860 --> 43:16.710
Killing Fu Ling isn't strange,

43:16.790 --> 43:19.300
but Chong Zhao is your personal disciple.

43:19.330 --> 43:20.690
You've been his teacher for years.

43:20.730 --> 43:22.080
Can you bear to be heartless?

43:22.110 --> 43:24.030
He already suspects me.

43:24.050 --> 43:25.610
If he must be killed, then so be it.

43:26.510 --> 43:28.360
Sometimes I'm quite curious.

43:28.380 --> 43:29.970
If the world's Eternals found out

43:30.000 --> 43:31.290
that their leader

43:31.310 --> 43:33.360
is such a ruthless

43:33.390 --> 43:35.110
and sinful person,

43:35.130 --> 43:36.600
how would they react?

43:38.540 --> 43:39.710
I have other things to do.

43:39.740 --> 43:41.100
Go back first.

43:41.120 --> 43:42.720
I have my own considerations

43:42.750 --> 43:44.180
for Bodhi Village's matters.

43:44.310 --> 43:45.750
You don't need to intervene

43:45.780 --> 43:47.340
or ask about it.

43:47.360 --> 43:47.950
Yes.

43:47.980 --> 43:49.870
I'll do as you say, Divine Maiden.

44:45.980 --> 44:48.140
Why do I always feel that you are

44:49.520 --> 44:51.430
different from before?
